{"tid":1490502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際文宣] 斬人事件 請廣傳！！！","createTime":"2019-08-20T06:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T06:24:56.000Z","uid":308885,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ef81d4314db435d7098a434b1e9f9d17a27aa06a","tid":1490502,"uid":308885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:23:16.000Z","msg":"見今朝有巴打話要人幫手整圖，將元朗、荃灣、將軍澳等斬人事件擺埋一齊，然後放上Twitter reddit廣傳<br />\n<br />\n我知道文宣組一定忙到爆哂肝，有時可能未咁快整得切，所以我睇完文宣教學post就試下幫手整<br />\n<br />\n第一次整文宣圖 整咗個幾兩個鐘 對住個丁屎咁大嘅電話moon整到眼都盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />整得唔好屌得細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/skZiYYB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FskZiYYB.png&h=5a8aca4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中文版仲整緊 如果呢張ok唔該各位share！！！<br />\n<br />\n同我一樣想幫手整文宣圖嘅巴絲睇呢兩個post!!!<br />\n<br />\n【教學】自己文宣自己整，自己香港自己救：唔駛Ps/Ai，免費整圖app Canva<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1365992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1365992</a><br />\n<br />\n【教學】自己文宣自己整（二）：喺 video 上/下面加字，用 Keynote / Powerpoint 就做到<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1485387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1485387</a>"},{"pid":"dd00d85b818953be345d7cef7f69a73fdcf3b4f3","tid":1490502,"uid":201064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:24:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}